 war where englanders two older sisters were born his father’s entire family was killed during the holocaust always interested in the stock market englander began trading stocks while in high school during college he interned at oppenheimer  co where his future brotherinlaw jack nash would eventually become president and chairman and at the new york stock exchange in  he graduated from new york university with a bs in finance his first fulltime job was with the wall street firm kaufmann alsberg  co he later enrolled in new york universitys mba program in the evenings but never completed the degree investment careeredit early business careeredit at kaufmann alsberg englander focused on trading convertible securities and options when the american stock exchange began to list options he purchased a seat on the exchange in  he formed a floor brokerage house ia englander  co in which he still owns a passive interest in  englander and his partner john mulheren jr started an investment firm called jamie securities co with a  million investment from the belzberg family of canada mulheren had previously worked as a trader for ivan boesky boesky was later convicted of insider trading and agreed to testify against mulheren in a plea deal to receive a lesser sentence in february  mulheren was arrested for carrying a loaded assault rifle mulheren was convicted of orchestrating illegal stock trades for boesky but the ruling was later overturned jamie securities was dissolved in  due to the negative publicity in the aftermath of mulherens situation englander was neither charged nor implicated in any way with mulherens activities start of his fundedit in  englander started millennium management llc with ronald shear  whom he knew from his time at the american stock exchange  with  million in seed money including  million from englander himself and another  million from the belzberg family the firm got off to a rough start and shear left in  since then englander has grown millennium into a plus billion dollar under management enterprise by using investment strategies like statistical arbitrage quantitative analysis fundamental longshort pairing merger arbitrage taking advantage of price differentials between a buyout target companys stock price and bid price and convertible arbitrage taking advantage of price differentials between a companys stock price and convertible bond or stock warrant price at any given time millennium holds thousands of investment positions and makes over  million trades on an average day at the end of  millennium had  employees in more than  offices around the world personal lifeedit englander is married to caryl née schechter englander they have three children wealth and philanthropyedit in  the englander foundation headed by englander and his wife donated  million to mostly jewish organizations and schools englander serves on the board of weill cornell medical college and the metropolitan council on jewish poverty referencesedit  a b c d forbes the worlds billionaires israel englander march   management millennium who we are  millennium management wwwmlpcom retrieved    israel englander forbes retrieved    a b c d e f g h i institutional investor izzy englanders growth strategy for millennium by stephen taub may    company history ia englander website march     den of thieves by james b stewart pp   a b c knaub matthias  dec  israel a englander transcript opalesque tv opalesque group retrieved  april    new york times paid notice deaths schechter samuel september    weill cornell medical college   our leadership  metropolitan council on jewish poverty wwwmetcouncilorg retrieved   external linksedit opalesquetv izzy englander interview part  retrieved march   retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleisraelenglanderoldidcareer categories  birthsamerican billionairesamerican derivatives tradersamerican hedge fund managersamerican investorsamerican money managersamerican philanthropistsamerican stock tradersbusine